"``send_file`` y ``send_from_directory`` son envolturas alrededor de las "
"implementaciones en ``werkzeug.utils``. :pr:`3828`"

#: ../../../CHANGES.rst:310
msgid ""
"Some ``send_file`` parameters have been renamed, the old names are "
